The paper proposes a technique for autonomous imitation learning, which involves developing a model from self-supervised experience and then learning a task by observing an expert without explicit action information. This involves aspects of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
